data.title: Jefferson Awards
data.meta_description: For over 50 years, the Jefferson Awards have been the highest and most prestigious honor recognizing public service in the United States.
data.text:
For over 50 years, the Jefferson Awards have been the highest and most prestigious honor recognizing public service in the United States. Past recipients include Oprah Winfrey, Former President Jimmy Carter, and Shaquille O'Neal.

About the Jefferson Awards

The Jefferson Awards represent the good that is happening all around us, in every community across the nation.
